{
 "cells": [
  {
   "source": [
    "# Inspect dataset"
   ],
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%config InlineBackend.figure_format = 'jpg'  # smaller mem footprint for page\n",
    "\n",
    "import das.npy_dir\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.style.use('ncb.mplstyle')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ds = das.npy_dir.load('tutorial_dataset.npy')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "source": [
    "## Print dataset information"
   ],
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {
    "tags": []
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "output_type": "stream",
     "name": "stdout",
     "text": [
      "Data:\n   test:\n      y_pulse: (3980001, 2)\n      y_sine: (3980001, 2)\n      x: (3980001, 1)\n      y: (3980001, 3)\n   train:\n      y_pulse: (20440005, 2)\n      y_sine: (20440005, 2)\n      x: (20440005, 1)\n      y: (20440005, 3)\n   val:\n      y_pulse: (4160001, 2)\n      y_sine: (4160001, 2)\n      x: (4160001, 1)\n      y: (4160001, 3)\n\nAttributes:\n    class_names: ['noise', 'pulse', 'sine']\n    class_names_pulse: ['noise', 'pulse']\n    class_names_sine: ['noise', 'sine']\n    class_types: ['segment', 'event', 'segment']\n    class_types_pulse: ['segment', 'event']\n    class_types_sine: ['segment', 'segment']\n    filename_endsample_test: []\n    filename_endsample_train: []\n    filename_endsample_val: []\n    filename_startsample_test: []\n    filename_startsample_train: []\n    filename_startsample_val: []\n    filename_train: []\n    filename_val: []\n    samplerate_x_Hz: 10000\n    samplerate_y_Hz: 10000\n    filename_test: []\n\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "print(ds)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "source": [
    "## Plot audio and annotations\n",
    "Plot, for the train, validation, and test set:\n",
    "- the audio\n",
    "- the training targets as line plots\n",
    "- the training targets as a pseudo-color plot (black - high probably, white - low probability).\n",
    "\n",
    "Adjust the start and duration, `start_seconds` and `duration_seconds`, to plot a part of the recording that should have annotated song. \n",
    "\n",
    "Things to check:\n",
    "- alignment between audio `x` and training targets `y`\n",
    "- width of events is appropriate\n",
    "- completeness of annotations\n",
    "\n",
    "In the example below the `test` set is incompletely annotated around 3.5 seconds."
   ],
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "output_type": "display_data",
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "<Figure size 2160x432 with 3 Axes>",
      "image/jpeg": "\n"
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     }
    },
    {
     "output_type": "display_data",
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "<Figure size 2160x432 with 3 Axes>",
      "image/jpeg": "\n"
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     }
    },
    {
     "output_type": "display_data",
     "data": {
      "text/plain": "<Figure size 2160x432 with 3 Axes>",
      "image/jpeg": "\n"
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     }
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "start_seconds = 2\n",
    "duration_seconds = 4\n",
    "for typ in ['train','val','test']:\n",
    "    t0_samples = int(start_seconds * ds.attrs['samplerate_x_Hz'])\n",
    "    t1_samples = int(t0_samples + duration_seconds * ds.attrs['samplerate_x_Hz'])\n",
    "\n",
    "    tx = np.arange(t0_samples, t1_samples) / ds.attrs['samplerate_x_Hz']\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(30, 6))\n",
    "    ax = plt.subplot(311)\n",
    "    plt.plot(tx, ds[typ]['x'][t0_samples:t1_samples], 'k')\n",
    "    plt.title(typ)\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('audio')\n",
    "\n",
    "    t0_samples = int(start_seconds * ds.attrs['samplerate_y_Hz'])\n",
    "    t1_samples = int(t0_samples + duration_seconds * ds.attrs['samplerate_y_Hz'])\n",
    "    ty = np.arange(t0_samples, t1_samples) / ds.attrs['samplerate_y_Hz']\n",
    "    plt.subplot(312, sharex=ax)\n",
    "    plt.plot(ty, ds[typ]['y'][t0_samples:t1_samples, :])\n",
    "    plt.legend(ds.attrs['class_names'])\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('annotations')\n",
    "    plt.ylim(0, 1.1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.subplot(313)\n",
    "    plt.imshow(ds[typ]['y'][t0_samples:t1_samples, :].T.astype(np.float), cmap='Greys')\n",
    "    plt.yticks(range(len(ds.attrs['class_names'])), labels=ds.attrs['class_names'])\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('annotations')\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    "
   ]
  }
 ],
